      "rationale": "Cadaveric validation study used 6 tibial tray geometry variants spanning the COU design space (plateau coverage 87–98%, cement mantle 2.5–4.5 mm). All 6 variants were directly validated against experimental strain-gauge data under ISO 14243-1 loading. Validation activities are fully representative of the COU. Level 3 achieved."
