        "description": "Material properties, geometry, and loading parameters used in the simulation must be traceable to directly measured values from the validation specimens. CT-derived bone modulus assignments must use the same Hounsfield unit-to-modulus mapping in both the validation model and the COU predictive model. Any discrepancies between experimental and simulation inputs must be documented and their effect on QoI quantified."
